TYPE HORIZON . — Lowermost Eocene, Ypresian (Sparnacian), level MP 7 of the mammal fauna of Dormaal. It has been demonstrated before that this amber is native, and very different from the Baltic amber in age, chemical composition and origin ( Feugueur 1963 ;
De Ploëg et al . 1998
;
Nel et al . 1999
).
